   "body" : "Adds a flag for peertimeout, defaults to 60 (the current hard-coded setting).\r\n\r\n- I saw that the p2p timeout was hard-coded and thought it should be configurable (if for some reason, the user has to minimize active open connections that aren't being utilized, or has a technical need to maintain long-running connections).\r\n- It also addresses #13518.\r\n- Making this configurable also lets use test more p2p scenarios; having too many slow tests is sometimes a reason to skip testing.",
